The invention provides a high pressure resistant input and output circuit for an electronic device. The high pressure resistant input and output circuit for the electronic device comprises a voltage reducing circuit, a first node, a first transistor, a second transistor and a control logic; the voltage reducing circuit which is in coupling connection with a signal connecting point of an electronic device is used for generating down regulation voltage according exterior voltage; the first node is used for providing first pressure; interior voltage output through the first node is served as the first voltage when interior voltage generated through an interior circuit is larger than the down regulation voltage; the down regulation voltage output through the first node is served as the first voltage when the down regulation voltage is larger than the interior voltage; a first end of the first transistor is in coupling connection with the signal connecting point and a control end is coupling connection with the first node; a first end of the second transistor is in coupling connection with a second end of the first transistor and a second end is in coupling connection with a fixed potential end; the control logic is operated according to the first voltage to control switching operation of the second transistor; the exterior voltage is larger than the interior voltage. The high pressure resistant input and output circuit for the electronic device can effectively avoid the problem that interior elements generate excessive electrical stress.
